The street, serving as the main artery of the scene, is flanked by buildings on both sides. These structures, predominantly in shades of gray and brown, exhibit a variety of architectural styles, hinting at the city's rich history and dynamic present.

The street itself is a hive of activity with cars and buses navigating their way, adding a sense of movement and life to the scene. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the backdrop of a gray, overcast sky, a common sight in many urban areas.

On the right side of the street, trees and bushes provide a touch of greenery, offering a stark contrast to the concrete jungle. Their presence softens the urban landscape, adding a sense of tranquility amidst the hustle and bustle.
